{"issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/3256", "repo": "rails", "body": "I succeeded with running Rails from GIthub, so I've added test for that shorthand.\r\n\r\n@josevalim Hm, you're right, `.to_s` should return string representation containg all information about object, not only name. I've changed it so that when body of a link respond to `.to_title`, result of that method is used as the body of link instead of the given body object itself.\r\n\r\n", "_id": {"$oid": "523838dbbd3543c15101004b"}, "issue_id": 3256, "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/2331886", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/3256#issuecomment-2331886", "updated_at": "2011-10-08T12:48:11Z", "user": {"subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl/subscriptions", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl/events{/privacy}", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl/repos", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl/gists{/gist_id}", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl", "login": "szymon-przybyl", "gravatar_id": "6eded0937cdaaf986756ececa8718e76", "html_url": "https://github.com/szymon-przybyl", "following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl/following{/other_user}", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl/received_events", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl/orgs", "avatar_url": "https://0.gravatar.com/avatar/6eded0937cdaaf986756ececa8718e76?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F1d3405e1744b9c93034a9a49781cc19f.png", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "id": 489586, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/szymon-przybyl/followers", "type": "User"}, "created_at": "2011-10-08T12:48:11Z", "id": 2331886, "owner": "rails"}
